{"word":"κώλυμα","slug":"κώλυμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κώλυμα</b></el> <el>(κώλῡμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κωλύω'><el>κωλύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a hindrance, impediment</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a defence against</i> a thing, <i>precaution</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}